An '''opal''' is the lowest level of semi-precious [[gem]]. Opals can be cut from [[uncut opal]]s with level 1 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 15 experience. While cutting opals, the player may accidentally crush an uncut opal into a [[crushed gem]] and will receive only 3.8 Crafting experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make opal jewellery.

